            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="constellation-fact-item">
          <span class="fact-icon">üìø</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Guru's Blessing</h3>
            <p>
              Jupiter's influence brings wisdom, righteousness (dharma), and the
              ability to guide others on their spiritual path.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="constellation-fact-item">
          <span class="fact-icon">üåü</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Moksha Karaka</h3>
            <p>
              In Jyotish, Sagittarius is associated with the 9th house of higher
              learning, philosophy, and spiritual liberation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="constellation-section-full"
      style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.05), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.2);"
    >
      <h2>Vedic Characteristics & Qualities</h2>
      <div
        style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;"
      >
        <div>
          <h3 style="color: #ffa500; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">
            Positive Traits (Sattvic)
          </h3>
          <ul
            style="color: #e0e0e0; line-height: 1.8; list-style: none; padding: 0;"
          >
            <li>‚Ä¢ Dharmic (righteous) nature</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Spiritual wisdom and intuition</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Natural teaching abilities</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Philosophical mindset</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Optimistic and adventurous</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Strong moral compass</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="color: #ffa500; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">
